short_description: zhejiang wuyi machinery co. ltd. is a machinery parts manufacturer based in china.
long_description: zhejiang wuyi machinery co., ltd. was established in 2002 (formerly zhejiang wuyi machinery factory, established in 1972), located in the national historical and cultural city of zhejiang province - cangzhou city (the hometown of movie star zhou xun). the company covers an area of 400,000 square meters and employs more than 5,000 people, including 538 engineers and technicians. the company is professionally equipped and has eleven of the world's most advanced german automatic chain knitting and welding production lines, two hanging assembly lines.
